    "description": "A trail around the village, on an unpaved road along four lakes (Țarina, Tăul Mare, Corna, Brazi) and 2 peaks (Rotundu și Șulei). See here the trail and discover more hiking or bike trails from Rosia Montana. Book accommodation, bikes, guided tours, camping.",
