      "type": "articles",
      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "Start from Casa Petri and head through the 'Țarina' land, along the 'Țarini' lake until you reach the the Weather Station from the 'Rotundu' Peak (the highest point from this trail). From here, on the left, you can see 'Tăul Mare' lake, which is our next destination. Head towards it and then climb on Șulei Peak. Have a break, enjoy the view and then continue to the 'Corna' Lake. Return in the village by the 'Piatra Corbului' (Raven Stone) and 'Brazi' Lake. The trail is on unpaved roads and is perfect for hiking or mountain bikes.",
